name: __EFieldVectorType
doc: TODO : Refactor these 3 enums to be in sync with the GetFieldTargetTypes

Vector_LinearForce: Add a vector field to the particles linear force.
Vector_LinearVelocity: Add a vector field to the particles linear velocity.
Vector_AngularVelocity: Add a vector field to the particles angular velocity.
Vector_AngularTorque: Add a vector field to the particles angular torque.
Vector_PositionTarget: Add a position constraint to the particles to follow a target position
Vector_InitialLinearVelocity: Set the geometry collection initial linear velocity
Vector_InitialAngularVelocity: Set the geometry collection initial angular velocity
Vector_LinearImpulse: Add a vector field affecting the particles linear impulse.
